\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf3\qj\tldot\tx6804{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi288\rtlch\af0\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f6\fs14\lang1033\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0{\ul\ulc0\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\b\loch\i\b L\'f4\'f8i 3 :}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0  Co\'f9 nh\'f6\'f5ng lu\'f9c na\'e8m ke\'e0 be\'e2n nhau, no\'f9i ta\'e2m t\'ecnh lo\'f8ng kho\'e2ng gia\'e1u nhau. Ca\'f8ng hie\'e5u nhau ta ca\'f8ng th\'f6\'f4ng nhau. Ca\'f8ng th\'f6\'f4ng nhau trong mo\'e4t mo\'e1i t\'ecnh: t\'ecnh \'f1a\'e1u tranh, g\'ecn n\'f6\'f4\'f9c non.(\'d1K)}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf3\qj\tldot\tx6804{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi288\rtlch\af0\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f6\fs14\lang1033\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0{\ul\ulc0\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\b\loch\i\b L\'f4\'f8i 4 :}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0  Co\'f9 nh\'f6\'f5ng lu\'f9c na\'e8m chung tra\'e4n tuye\'e1n, xe\'f9 kha\'ean m\'ecnh lie\'e0n ba\'eang ve\'e1t th\'f6\'f4ng. Choa\'f8ng ca\'f9nh tay o\'e2m ng\'f6\'f4\'f8i ba\'efn ta. La\'f8n mo\'e2i xanh ch\'f6a ta\'f8n nu\'ef c\'f6\'f4\'f8i. Do\'f8ng ma\'f9u t\'f6\'f4i tra\'f8n \'f6\'f4\'f9c tay.(\'d1K)}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf3\qj\tldot\tx6804{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi288\rtlch\af0\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f6\fs14\lang1033\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0{\ul\ulc0\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\b\loch\i\b L\'f4\'f8i 5 :}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0  Tra\'fbi na\'eam tha\'f9ng \'f1\'f4\'f8i vui chie\'e1n \'f1a\'e1u. Su\'f9ng be\'e2n m\'ecnh lo\'f8ng ha\'eang gie\'e1t Ta\'e2y. Do\'f8ng ma\'f9u tuo\'e2n nh\'f6ng lo\'f8ng kho\'e2ng nao.Du\'f8 gian nan kho\'e2ng mo\'e4t b\'f6\'f4\'f9c lu\'f8i.Nghe\'f8o su\'f9ng g\'f6\'f4m, gia\'f8u chie\'e1n co\'e2ng.(\'d1K)}
