\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf3\qj\tldot\tx6804{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi288\rtlch\af0\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f6\fs14\lang1033\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0 \'d1e\'efp bie\'e1t bao vo\'f8ng tay tha\'e2n a\'f9i. E\'c2m d\'f2u nh\'f6 t\'ecnh ye\'e2u trong sa\'f9ng. Cuo\'e4c \'f1\'f4\'f8i tha\'e1y nga\'f8y ca\'f8ng de\'e3 th\'f6\'f4ng. T\'ecnh ng\'f6\'f4\'f8i tha\'e1y ca\'f8ng tr\'ecu me\'e1n h\'f4n. }
