\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf3\qj\tldot\tx6804{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi288\rtlch\af0\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f6\fs14\lang1033\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0 Me\'ef \'f4i ! con th\'f6\'f4ng me\'ef qua\'f9 me\'ef \'f4i. Con vo\'e2 t\'ecnh qua\'f9 pha\'fbi kho\'e2ng khi ba\'e1y la\'e2u h\'f4\'f8 h\'f6\'f5ng me\'ef. Bao nga\'f8y qua do\'e3i t\'ecm nh\'f6\'f5ng cha\'e2n tr\'f4\'f8i xa. Co\'f5i \'f1\'f4\'f8i \'f1a\'e9m nay ma\'f8 que\'e2n co\'f8n \'f1o\'f9 be\'e2n ta me\'ef gia\'f8.  Co\'f8n na\'f8o que\'e2n nh\'f6\'fbng nga\'f8y la\'f8m lu\'efng trie\'e0n mie\'e2n. Th
