\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf3\qj\tldot\tx6804{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi288\rtlch\af0\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f6\fs14\lang1033\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0 Ba\'f8ng hoa\'f8ng thay \'f1e\'e2m nay con m\'f4 tha\'e1y me\'ef, Me\'ef \'f1i nh\'f6 a\'f9ng ma\'e2y bay cuo\'e1i tr\'f4\'f8i. Ba\'e2y gi\'f4\'f8 d\'f6\'f4\'f8ng nh\'f6 con r\'f4i n\'f6\'f4\'f9c ma\'e9t. S\'f4\'ef a\'f9ng ma\'e2y bay qua tr\'f4\'f8i co\'f8n day d\'f6\'f9t bao lo\'e3i la\'e0m. Nga\'f8y a\'e1y \'f1a\'f5 la\'f8m \'f1au lo\'f8ng me\'ef ye\'e2u !}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf3\qj\tldot\tx6804{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi288\rtlch\af0\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f6\fs14\lang1033\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0 Trong lo\'f8ng con a\'e1p u\'fb h\'ecnh a\'fbnh me\'ef ye\'e2u. A\'f9o s\'f4\'f8n mo\'e4t \'f1\'f4\'f8i cha\'e9t chiu hy sing da\'e3u cho co\'f9 nghe\'f8o. T\'f6\'f8 nga\'f8n x\'f6a bo\'f9ng h\'ecnh ng\'f6\'f4\'f8i me\'ef Vie\'e4t Nam. Da\'e3u la\'f8 \'f1\'f4n s\'f4 ba\'e0n ha\'f8n va\'e3n ra\'efng ng\'f4\'f8i v\'f4\'f9i th\'f4\'f8i gian.}
