\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf3\qj\tldot\tx6804{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi288\rtlch\af0\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f6\fs14\lang1033\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0 Me\'ef que\'e2 nga\'f8y \'f1o\'f9, l\'f6ng cong d\'f6\'f4\'f9i m\'f6a bay. Ca\'f9nh tay ga\'e0y mo\'fbng manh ma\'f8u ma\'e2y. Tie\'e3n con \'f1i me\'ef ve\'e0 la\'ebng le\'f5. La\'f9 kho\'e2 r\'f4i be\'e2n \'f1\'f4\'f8i me\'ef gia\'f8. T\'f6\'f8ng \'f1e\'e2m gio\'f9 m\'f6a nh\'f6 vo\'e2 t\'ecnh qua.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf3\qj\tldot\tx6804{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi288\rtlch\af0\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f6\fs14\lang1033\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0 Co\'f8n \'f1o\'f9 v\'f4\'f9i nh\'f6\'f5ng tie\'e1c nuo\'e1i. Co\'f8n \'f1o\'f9 nh\'f6\'f5ng tie\'e1ng la\'f9 r\'f4i. Ma\'f9i tranh x\'f6a \'f1o\'e2i la\'e0n con ve\'e0. Ng\'f6\'f4\'f8i ne\'e1u \'f6\'f4\'f9c muo\'e1n qua\'f9 l\'f4\'f9n. La\'efc lo\'e1i gi\'f6\'f5a nh\'f6\'f5ng bie\'e5n kh\'f4i. Cho\'e1n que\'e2 x\'f6a me\'ef ch\'f4\'f8 mong ma\'f5i}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf3\qj\tldot\tx6804{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi288\rtlch\af0\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f6\fs14\lang1033\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs14\lang1033\i0\b0 Chie\'e0u nay la\'ebng le\'f5 con nghe tie\'e1ng ru x\'f6a. B\'f6\'f4\'f9c cha\'e2n ve\'e0 d\'f6\'f4\'f9i hie\'e2n chie\'e0u m\'f6a. Kho\'f9i s\'f6\'f4ng tan mo\'e4t nga\'f8y la\'ebng le\'f5. Ma\'f9i tranh x\'f6a lang thang kho\'e2ng co\'f8n me\'ef gia\'f8. Co\'f8n \'f1a\'e2y b\'f6\'f4\'f9c cha\'e2n con lang thang chie\'e0u m\'f6a. }
